Class PlayGroundOwner

  • java.lang.Object
    • software.User
      • software.PlayGroundOwner
  • public class PlayGroundOwner
extends User
    They are the owner of the playgrounds and they are the ones who offer it to the system in order to make money from it . He can create a profile if he doesn't have it, or he can log in if he has one . He can add stadiums and everything related to them, and he can also do updates for them .
